              </div>
              <div class="callout-body">
                <strong>Egypt's renewable-energy advantage</strong>
                <p>Egypt's aluminium industry draws on hydroelectric power from the Aswan High Dam, and the country is commissioning 1 GW of additional green power specifically for aluminium manufacturing. Lower embedded emissions mean fewer CBAM certificates your business needs to purchase. <a href="/en/cbam-guide/">Read our full CBAM guide →</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

