            <h2>Packaging & shipping</h2>
            <p>
              ADC12 ingots are bundled with high-tensile steel straps, palletised for container
              loading, and shrink-wrapped where required. Standard bundle weights are configurable
              between 500 kg and 1,000 kg to match your handling equipment.
            </p>
