              <li><strong>40ft container:</strong> ~24–26 tonnes net (heavy-load configuration)</li>
              <li><strong>European ports served:</strong> Rotterdam, Hamburg, Antwerp, Genoa, Barcelona, Felixstowe</li>
              <li><strong>Incoterms offered:</strong> FOB Egyptian port, CIF named EU port, CFR, Ex-Works</li>
              <li><strong>Lead time:</strong> 10–30 days from order confirmation to EU port arrival</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Full export documentation included with every shipment: Commercial Invoice, Packing
